{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/samSelectDetailRegion","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion","roleHeading":"Function","symbolKind":"func","modules":[{"name":"DotFaceLite"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SamColorImage","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/sam_color_image"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"image","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"const","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"int","preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selectedBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":");"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"should lie fully inside the input image.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or ","type":"text"},{"code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite"]]},"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/dotfacelite\/samselectdetailregion"]}],"references":{"doc://DotFaceLite/documentation/DotFaceLite/sam_color_image":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceLite\/documentation\/DotFaceLite\/sam_color_image","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"sam_color_image","url":"\/documentation\/dotfacelite\/sam_color_image","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"sam_color_image"}]},"doc://DotFaceLite/documentation/DotFaceLite":{"kind":"symbol","identifier"